1
00:00:07,166 --> 00:00:09,417
Katara: WATER...

2
00:00:09,458 --> 00:00:11,291
EARTH...

3
00:00:11,333 --> 00:00:13,709
FIRE...

4
00:00:13,750 --> 00:00:15,792
AIR.

5
00:00:15,834 --> 00:00:20,208
LONG AGO, THE 4 NATIONS
LIVED TOGETHER IN HARMONY.

6
00:00:20,250 --> 00:00:24,792
THEN, EVERYTHING CHANGED
WHEN THE FIRE NATION ATTACKED.

7
00:00:24,834 --> 00:00:27,458
ONLY THE AVATAR,
MASTER OF ALL 4 ELEMENTS,

8
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:29,000
COULD STOP THEM.

9
00:00:29,041 --> 00:00:30,792
BUT WHEN THE WORLD
NEEDED HIM MOST,

10
00:00:30,834 --> 00:00:32,000
HE VANISHED.

11
00:00:32,041 --> 00:00:34,083
100 YEARS PASSED,

12
00:00:34,125 --> 00:00:36,125
AND MY BROTHER AND I
DISCOVERED THE NEW AVATAR--

13
00:00:36,166 --> 00:00:38,125
AN AIRBENDER NAMED AANG.

14
00:00:38,166 --> 00:00:40,041
AND ALTHOUGH HIS AIRBENDING
SKILLS ARE GREAT,

15
00:00:40,083 --> 00:00:42,875
HE HAS A LOT TO LEARN BEFORE
HE'S READY TO SAVE ANYONE.

16
00:00:42,917 --> 00:00:44,667
Aang: OOF.

17
00:00:44,709 --> 00:00:46,583
Katara: BUT I BELIEVE AANG
CAN SAVE THE WORLD.

18
00:00:57,291 --> 00:00:59,375
Katara: THE NORTHERN
WATER TRIBE.

19
00:00:59,417 --> 00:01:01,375
WE'RE FINALLY HERE.

20
00:01:01,417 --> 00:01:04,792
Zhao: THERE'S A REASON THEY'VE
SURVIVED 100 YEARS OF WAR.

21
00:01:04,834 --> 00:01:07,834
WE'LL NEED A MASSIVE
INVASION FORCE.

22
00:01:07,875 --> 00:01:09,458
THE SPIRITS!

23
00:01:09,500 --> 00:01:10,917
MAYBE I CAN FIND THEM
AND GET THEIR HELP!

24
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:18,208
Uncle: THE WATERBENDERS
DRAW THEIR POWER
FROM THE MOON.

25
00:01:18,250 --> 00:01:20,166
Zhao: OH, I'M WELL AWARE
OF THE MOON PROBLEM,

26
00:01:20,208 --> 00:01:23,041
AND I AM WORKING
ON A SOLUTION.

27
00:01:23,083 --> 00:01:25,333
Uncle: ZHAO DOESN'T
SUSPECT A THING.

28
00:01:25,375 --> 00:01:27,959
STAY HIDDEN UNTIL WE GET
TO THE NORTH POLE,

29
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:30,041
AND THE AVATAR WILL BE YOURS.

30
00:01:34,041 --> 00:01:36,041
HE'S CROSSING
INTO THE SPIRIT WORLD.

31
00:01:36,083 --> 00:01:37,834
HE'LL BE FINE
AS LONG AS WE DON'T
MOVE HIS BODY.

32
00:01:41,709 --> 00:01:42,750
UNH!

33
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,917
Katara: I CAN'T
BELIEVE I LOST HIM.

34
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:06,917
Sokka: YOU DID
EVERYTHING YOU COULD.

35
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,583
AND NOW WE NEED TO
DO EVERYTHING WE CAN

36
00:02:08,625 --> 00:02:10,166
TO GET HIM BACK.

37
00:02:10,208 --> 00:02:11,208
ZUKO CAN'T HAVE
GOTTEN FAR.

38
00:02:11,250 --> 00:02:12,625
WE'LL FIND HIM.

39
00:02:12,667 --> 00:02:14,166
AANG'S GONNA BE FINE.

40
00:02:14,208 --> 00:02:15,041
OK.

41
00:02:19,917 --> 00:02:21,125
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

42
00:02:21,166 --> 00:02:22,417
YOU STAY HERE, MOMO--

43
00:02:22,458 --> 00:02:23,750
IN CASE AANG
COMES BACK.

44
00:02:23,792 --> 00:02:24,834
YIP, YIP!

45
00:02:49,125 --> 00:02:52,333
Man: OM.

46
00:02:52,375 --> 00:02:54,583
OM.

47
00:02:54,625 --> 00:02:56,125
HELLO?

48
00:02:56,166 --> 00:02:57,542
I'M SORRY
TO DISTURB YOU.

49
00:02:57,583 --> 00:02:59,166
I JUST REALLY
NEED TO FIND

50
00:02:59,208 --> 00:03:00,250
THE MOON
AND THE OCEAN SPIRITS.

51
00:03:00,291 --> 00:03:02,041
GO AWAY.

52
00:03:04,709 --> 00:03:06,083
YOU'RE STILL HERE?

53
00:03:06,125 --> 00:03:07,500
YES, I NEED--

54
00:03:07,542 --> 00:03:10,125
OM!

55
00:03:10,166 --> 00:03:12,041
PERHAPS THAT THING
WILL HELP YOU.

56
00:03:12,083 --> 00:03:12,917
CHASE IT!

57
00:03:15,125 --> 00:03:16,083
[SIGHS]

58
00:03:16,125 --> 00:03:16,792
FINALLY.

59
00:03:22,500 --> 00:03:25,208
[SCREAMS]

60
00:03:25,250 --> 00:03:25,959
COME BACK!

61
00:03:29,041 --> 00:03:31,083
HELLO, AANG.

62
00:03:31,125 --> 00:03:32,041
ROKU?!

63
00:03:39,083 --> 00:03:40,583
HUH?!

64
00:03:40,625 --> 00:03:42,250
[GASPING]

65
00:03:57,166 --> 00:03:58,083
SHELTER!

66
00:04:09,125 --> 00:04:11,792
ROKU, THE WATER TRIBE
IS UNDER ATTACK!

67
00:04:11,834 --> 00:04:13,667
I NEED TO FIND THE OCEAN
AND THE MOON SPIRITS.

68
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:19,333
THE OCEAN AND THE MOON
ARE ANCIENT SPIRITS--

69
00:04:19,375 --> 00:04:22,125
THEY CROSSED OVER
FROM THE SPIRIT WORLD

70
00:04:22,166 --> 00:04:25,375
TO THE MORTAL WORLD
VERY NEAR THE BEGINNING.

71
00:04:25,417 --> 00:04:28,041
THERE IS ONLY ONE
SPIRIT I KNOW OF

72
00:04:28,083 --> 00:04:30,667
WHO IS OLD ENOUGH
TO REMEMBER...

73
00:04:30,709 --> 00:04:32,166
WHO?

74
00:04:32,208 --> 00:04:34,875
THE SPIRIT'S
NAME IS KOH,

75
00:04:34,917 --> 00:04:37,000
BUT HE IS VERY
DANGEROUS--

76
00:04:37,041 --> 00:04:40,500
THEY CALL HIM
"THE FACE STEALER."

77
00:04:40,542 --> 00:04:42,125
WHEN YOU SPEAK WITH HIM,

78
00:04:42,166 --> 00:04:44,417
YOU MUST BE
VERY CAREFUL

79
00:04:44,458 --> 00:04:46,667
TO SHOW NO
EMOTION AT ALL--

80
00:04:46,709 --> 00:04:49,583
NOT THE SLIGHTEST
EXPRESSION--

81
00:04:49,625 --> 00:04:52,041
OR HE WILL STEAL
YOUR FACE.

82
00:05:11,458 --> 00:05:13,208
I FINALLY HAVE YOU,

83
00:05:13,250 --> 00:05:16,291
BUT I CAN'T GET YOU HOME
BECAUSE OF THIS BLIZZARD.

84
00:05:16,333 --> 00:05:18,500
THERE'S ALWAYS SOMETHING.

85
00:05:18,542 --> 00:05:20,125
NOT THAT YOU WOULD
UNDERSTAND.

86
00:05:20,166 --> 00:05:22,000
YOU'RE LIKE MY SISTER.

87
00:05:22,041 --> 00:05:24,291
EVERYTHING ALWAYS
CAME EASY TO HER.

88
00:05:24,333 --> 00:05:26,458
SHE'S A FIREBENDING
PRODIGY...

89
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:28,333
AND EVERYONE ADORES HER.

90
00:05:28,375 --> 00:05:30,625
MY FATHER SAYS SHE
WAS BORN LUCKY.

91
00:05:30,667 --> 00:05:33,250
HE SAYS I WAS LUCKY
TO BE BORN.

92
00:05:33,291 --> 00:05:35,291
I DON'T NEED
LUCK, THOUGH--

93
00:05:35,333 --> 00:05:37,125
I DON'T WANT IT.

94
00:05:37,166 --> 00:05:38,792
I'VE ALWAYS HAD TO
STRUGGLE AND FIGHT,

95
00:05:38,834 --> 00:05:40,625
AND THAT'S MADE
ME STRONG...

96
00:05:40,667 --> 00:05:42,125
IT'S MADE ME WHO I AM.

97
00:06:12,834 --> 00:06:14,000
Uncle: I DON'T NEED
TO REMIND YOU

98
00:06:14,041 --> 00:06:15,709
WE HAVE
A TIME LIMIT.

99
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:17,542
IF WE DON'T DEFEAT
THE WATER TRIBE

100
00:06:17,583 --> 00:06:19,750
BEFORE THE FULL
MOON RISES,

101
00:06:19,792 --> 00:06:21,333
THEY WILL BE
UNDEFEATABLE.

102
00:06:21,375 --> 00:06:24,875
I ASSURE YOU--
I HAVE EVERYTHING
UNDER CONTROL.

103
00:06:24,917 --> 00:06:27,542
I INTEND TO REMOVE
THE MOON AS A FACTOR.

104
00:06:27,583 --> 00:06:29,000
REMOVE THE MOON?

105
00:06:29,041 --> 00:06:30,333
HOW?

106
00:06:30,375 --> 00:06:32,875
- ADMIRAL CHOI!

107
00:06:32,917 --> 00:06:34,583
PREPARE TO MEET
YOUR FATE!

108
00:06:36,166 --> 00:06:38,041
WHOA!

109
00:06:38,083 --> 00:06:39,000
[SPLASH]

110
00:06:39,041 --> 00:06:40,750
AS I WAS SAYING.

111
00:06:40,792 --> 00:06:42,500
YEARS AGO,
I STUMBLED UPON

112
00:06:42,542 --> 00:06:45,000
A GREAT AND POWERFUL SECRET--

113
00:06:45,041 --> 00:06:48,417
THE IDENTITY OF THE MOON
SPIRIT'S MORTAL FORM.

114
00:06:48,458 --> 00:06:49,709
WHAT?!

115
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:51,250
I WAS A YOUNG LIEUTENANT

116
00:06:51,291 --> 00:06:54,083
SERVING UNDER GENERAL XU
IN THE EARTH KINGDOM.

117
00:06:54,125 --> 00:06:55,583
I DISCOVERED
A HIDDEN LIBRARY--

118
00:06:55,625 --> 00:06:57,625
UNDERGROUND, IN FACT.

119
00:06:57,667 --> 00:07:00,458
I TORE THROUGH
SCROLL AFTER SCROLL.

120
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:03,166
ONE OF THEM CONTAINED
A DETAILED ILLUSTRATION--

121
00:07:03,208 --> 00:07:07,041
AND THE WORDS "MOON"
AND "OCEAN."

122
00:07:07,083 --> 00:07:09,667
I KNEW THEN THAT THESE
SPIRITS COULD BE FOUND...

123
00:07:09,709 --> 00:07:11,917
AND KILLED...

124
00:07:11,959 --> 00:07:14,875
AND THAT IT WAS MY
DESTINY TO DO SO.

125
00:07:14,917 --> 00:07:17,875
ZHAO, THE SPIRITS
ARE NOT TO BE
TRIFLED WITH!

126
00:07:17,917 --> 00:07:22,125
YES, YES, I KNOW YOU
FEAR THE SPIRITS, IROH--

127
00:07:22,166 --> 00:07:23,750
I HAVE HEARD RUMOURS
ABOUT YOUR JOURNEY

128
00:07:23,792 --> 00:07:25,625
INTO THE SPIRIT WORLD.

129
00:07:25,667 --> 00:07:28,125
BUT THE OCEAN AND MOON
GAVE UP THEIR IMMORTALITY

130
00:07:28,166 --> 00:07:30,166
TO BECOME A PART
OF OUR WORLD.

131
00:07:30,208 --> 00:07:33,083
AND NOW THEY WILL
FACE THE CONSEQUENCES.

132
00:07:49,375 --> 00:07:51,083
[CHATTERING]

133
00:07:51,125 --> 00:07:52,166
[GASPS]

134
00:07:52,208 --> 00:07:53,959
PHEW!

135
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,208
YOU'RE JUST
A CURLY-TAILED BLUENOSE.

136
00:07:57,208 --> 00:07:58,875
[GASPS]

137
00:08:01,125 --> 00:08:03,000
SHOW NO FEAR.

138
00:08:03,041 --> 00:08:04,583
SHOW NO EMOTION AT ALL.

139
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:19,500
HELLO?

140
00:08:19,542 --> 00:08:21,250
I'M LOOKING FOR
A SPIRIT NAMED KOH.

141
00:08:34,542 --> 00:08:35,583
WELCOME.

142
00:08:38,834 --> 00:08:40,083
THANK YOU.

143
00:08:40,125 --> 00:08:43,041
MY OLD FRIEND,
THE AVATAR--

144
00:08:43,083 --> 00:08:46,000
IT'S BEEN
A LONG TIME.

145
00:08:46,041 --> 00:08:47,375
YOU KNOW ME?

146
00:08:47,417 --> 00:08:50,000
HOW COULD I FORGET YOU?

147
00:08:50,041 --> 00:08:51,625
ONE OF YOUR PREVIOUS
INCARNATIONS

148
00:08:51,667 --> 00:08:53,333
TRIED TO SLAY ME--

149
00:08:53,375 --> 00:08:56,166
MAYBE 800 OR 900
YEARS AGO.

150
00:08:56,208 --> 00:08:58,625
I DIDN'T KNOW THAT.

151
00:08:58,667 --> 00:09:02,417
WHY DID HE--OR I--
TRY TO KILL YOU?

152
00:09:02,458 --> 00:09:04,792
OH, IT WAS
SOMETHING ABOUT

153
00:09:04,834 --> 00:09:06,667
STEALING THE FACE
OF SOMEONE YOU LOVED.

154
00:09:11,583 --> 00:09:14,500
[LAUGHING]

155
00:09:14,542 --> 00:09:17,458
OF COURSE, THAT'S
ALL BEHIND US.

156
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:19,333
WHY SHOULD I HOLD
A GRUDGE AGAINST YOU

157
00:09:19,375 --> 00:09:20,917
FOR SOMETHING
IN A PAST LIFE?

158
00:09:20,959 --> 00:09:22,291
AFTER ALL--

159
00:09:22,333 --> 00:09:24,041
YOU'RE A DIFFERENT
PERSON NOW.

160
00:09:24,083 --> 00:09:26,542
YOU'VE COME TO ME
WITH A NEW FACE.

161
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:34,125
GUESS WE'LL BE
HERE AWHILE.

162
00:09:37,709 --> 00:09:39,208
Yue: DON'T WORRY.

163
00:09:39,250 --> 00:09:40,333
PRINCE ZUKO CAN'T
BE GETTING TOO FAR

164
00:09:40,375 --> 00:09:42,333
IN THIS WEATHER.

165
00:09:42,375 --> 00:09:44,500
I'M NOT WORRIED
THEY'LL GET AWAY
IN THE BLIZZARD.

166
00:09:44,542 --> 00:09:46,667
I'M WORRIED
THAT THEY WON'T.

167
00:09:46,709 --> 00:09:48,208
Sokka: THEY'RE NOT GONNA
DIE IN THIS BLIZZARD.

168
00:09:48,250 --> 00:09:49,834
IF WE KNOW ANYTHING,

169
00:09:49,875 --> 00:09:51,375
IT'S THAT ZUKO
NEVER GIVES UP.

170
00:09:51,417 --> 00:09:54,458
THEY'LL SURVIVE--
AND WE'LL FIND THEM.

171
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:56,291
IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME

172
00:09:56,333 --> 00:09:59,041
SINCE I'VE ADDED A CHILD'S
FACE TO MY COLLECTION.

173
00:09:59,083 --> 00:10:00,250
SO...

174
00:10:00,291 --> 00:10:02,625
HOW MAY I HELP YOU?

175
00:10:02,667 --> 00:10:05,208
Aang: I NEED TO FIND
THE MOON AND THE OCEAN.

176
00:10:05,250 --> 00:10:09,041
THEIR SPIRIT NAMES
ARE "TUI" AND "LA--"

177
00:10:09,083 --> 00:10:11,625
PUSH AND PULL.

178
00:10:11,667 --> 00:10:13,667
AND THAT HAS
BEEN THE NATURE

179
00:10:13,709 --> 00:10:16,500
OF THEIR RELATIONSHIP
FOR ALL TIME.

180
00:10:16,542 --> 00:10:19,041
PLEASE, HELP ME
FIND THEM.

181
00:10:19,083 --> 00:10:21,208
AN ENTIRE CULTURE
COULD BE DESTROYED

182
00:10:21,250 --> 00:10:22,917
IF I DON'T
GET THEIR HELP.

183
00:10:22,959 --> 00:10:26,041
OH, YOU THINK YOU
NEED THEIR HELP?

184
00:10:26,083 --> 00:10:29,667
ACTUALLY, IT'S QUITE
THE OTHER WAY AROUND.

185
00:10:29,709 --> 00:10:32,417
SOMEONE IS GOING
TO KILL THEM!

186
00:10:32,458 --> 00:10:34,208
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

187
00:10:34,250 --> 00:10:36,083
HOW CAN I FIND THEM
AND PROTECT THEM?

188
00:10:36,125 --> 00:10:39,667
YOU'VE ALREADY MET
THEM, ACTUALLY.

189
00:10:39,709 --> 00:10:43,792
TUI AND LA--
YOUR MOON AND OCEAN--

190
00:10:43,834 --> 00:10:46,959
HAVE ALWAYS CIRCLED EACH
OTHER IN AN ETERNAL DANCE.

191
00:10:47,041 --> 00:10:49,125
THEY BALANCE EACH OTHER:

192
00:10:49,166 --> 00:10:52,166
PUSH AND PULL,
LIFE AND DEATH,

193
00:10:52,208 --> 00:10:54,709
GOOD AND EVIL...

194
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:57,083
YIN AND YANG.

195
00:11:01,208 --> 00:11:02,041
THE KOI FISH!

196
00:11:04,583 --> 00:11:06,625
I MUST BE GOING NOW.

197
00:11:06,667 --> 00:11:08,333
WE'LL MEET AGAIN.

198
00:11:14,250 --> 00:11:15,792
THE SPIRITS
ARE IN TROUBLE!

199
00:11:15,834 --> 00:11:17,250
I NEED TO GET BACK
TO THE PHYSICAL WORLD!

200
00:11:17,291 --> 00:11:20,959
A FRIEND IS HERE
TO GUIDE YOU BACK.

201
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:21,959
HEI BAI!

202
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,417
[MEWS]

203
00:11:29,667 --> 00:11:31,083
[SCREAMING]

204
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,417
[SCREAMS]

205
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:14,250
WE'LL BE
FOLLOWING THIS MAP

206
00:12:14,291 --> 00:12:16,125
TO A VERY
SPECIAL LOCATION.

207
00:12:16,166 --> 00:12:18,166
AND WHEN
WE GET THERE...

208
00:12:18,208 --> 00:12:20,041
WE'RE GOING FISHING.

209
00:12:23,959 --> 00:12:25,542
THIS IS WHERE
I CAME IN...

210
00:12:25,583 --> 00:12:26,959
BUT HOW DO I GET BACK?

211
00:12:34,542 --> 00:12:35,792
GOOD RIDDANCE.

212
00:12:37,125 --> 00:12:38,792
[SCREAMS]

213
00:12:41,291 --> 00:12:43,208
MOMO!

214
00:12:43,250 --> 00:12:44,834
MOMO?

215
00:12:44,875 --> 00:12:45,959
OH, NO...

216
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:46,834
WHERE'S MY BODY?

217
00:12:53,834 --> 00:12:55,000
LOOK!

218
00:12:55,041 --> 00:12:56,000
THAT'S GOT TO
BE AANG!

219
00:12:56,041 --> 00:12:57,333
YIP, YIP!

220
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,834
HUH?!

221
00:13:05,250 --> 00:13:07,125
[STRAINING]

222
00:13:07,166 --> 00:13:08,208
WELCOME BACK.

223
00:13:08,250 --> 00:13:09,250
GOOD TO BE BACK.

224
00:13:14,166 --> 00:13:16,083
[GRUNTING]

225
00:13:16,125 --> 00:13:19,542
THAT WON'T BE
ENOUGH TO ESCAPE.

226
00:13:19,583 --> 00:13:20,250
APPA!

227
00:13:24,166 --> 00:13:25,333
WHOA!

228
00:13:25,375 --> 00:13:26,500
HERE FOR A REMATCH?

229
00:13:26,542 --> 00:13:28,250
TRUST ME, ZUKO,

230
00:13:28,291 --> 00:13:30,208
IT'S NOT GOING TO
BE MUCH OF A MATCH.

231
00:13:36,125 --> 00:13:38,834
HEY, THIS IS
SOME QUALITY ROPE.

232
00:13:38,875 --> 00:13:40,500
WE NEED TO GET
TO THE OASIS!

233
00:13:40,542 --> 00:13:41,625
THE SPIRITS
ARE IN TROUBLE.

234
00:13:46,834 --> 00:13:49,166
WAIT--WE CAN'T JUST
LEAVE HIM HERE.

235
00:13:49,208 --> 00:13:50,125
SURE, WE CAN.

236
00:13:50,166 --> 00:13:51,125
LET'S GO.

237
00:13:51,166 --> 00:13:52,667
NO.

238
00:13:52,709 --> 00:13:53,792
IF WE LEAVE HIM,
HE'LL DIE.

239
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:58,041
[GRUNTS]

240
00:13:58,083 --> 00:13:59,333
Sokka: YEAH, THIS MAKES
A LOT OF SENSE--

241
00:13:59,375 --> 00:14:01,041
LET'S BRING THE GUY

242
00:14:01,083 --> 00:14:02,041
WHO'S CONSTANTLY
TRYING TO KILL US.

243
00:14:24,959 --> 00:14:26,375
[SCREAMING]

244
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,083
[GROANING]

245
00:14:34,125 --> 00:14:35,166
ARE YOU OK?

246
00:14:35,208 --> 00:14:36,709
I FEEL FAINT.

247
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:37,959
I FEEL IT, TOO.

248
00:14:40,166 --> 00:14:42,125
THE MOON SPIRIT
IS IN TROUBLE.

249
00:14:42,166 --> 00:14:44,417
I OWE THE MOON
SPIRIT MY LIFE.

250
00:14:44,458 --> 00:14:45,542
WHAT DO
YOU MEAN?

251
00:14:45,583 --> 00:14:47,000
WHEN I WAS BORN,

252
00:14:47,041 --> 00:14:49,750
I WAS VERY SICK
AND VERY WEAK.

253
00:14:49,792 --> 00:14:52,250
MOST BABIES CRY
WHEN THEY'RE BORN,

254
00:14:52,291 --> 00:14:54,542
BUT I WAS BORN AS
IF I WERE ASLEEP,

255
00:14:54,583 --> 00:14:56,083
MY EYES CLOSED.

256
00:14:56,125 --> 00:14:59,125
OUR HEALERS DID
EVERYTHING THEY COULD.

257
00:14:59,166 --> 00:15:00,875
THEY TOLD MY
MOTHER AND FATHER

258
00:15:00,917 --> 00:15:03,208
I WAS GOING TO DIE.

259
00:15:03,250 --> 00:15:06,417
MY FATHER PLEADED WITH
THE SPIRITS TO SAVE ME.

260
00:15:06,458 --> 00:15:08,834
THAT NIGHT--BENEATH
THE FULL MOON--

261
00:15:08,875 --> 00:15:12,458
HE BROUGHT ME TO THE OASIS
AND PLACED ME IN THE POND.

262
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:14,750
MY DARK HAIR TURNED WHITE.

263
00:15:14,792 --> 00:15:17,333
I OPENED MY EYES
AND BEGAN TO CRY...

264
00:15:17,375 --> 00:15:18,750
WAAH!

265
00:15:18,792 --> 00:15:20,834
AND THEY KNEW I WOULD LIVE.

266
00:15:20,875 --> 00:15:23,000
THAT'S WHY MY MOTHER
NAMED ME YUE,

267
00:15:23,041 --> 00:15:24,291
FOR THE MOON.

268
00:15:27,208 --> 00:15:31,208
Zhao: I AM A LEGEND NOW.

269
00:15:31,250 --> 00:15:33,333
THE FIRE NATION
WILL FOR GENERATIONS

270
00:15:33,375 --> 00:15:35,291
TELL STORIES ABOUT
THE GREAT ZHAO,

271
00:15:35,333 --> 00:15:38,166
WHO DARKENED THE MOON.

272
00:15:38,208 --> 00:15:41,208
THEY WILL CALL ME
ZHAO THE CONQUEROR...

273
00:15:41,250 --> 00:15:43,208
ZHAO THE MOON-SLAYER...

274
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:46,083
ZHAO THE INVINCIBLE!

275
00:15:46,125 --> 00:15:47,125
[CHITTERING]

276
00:15:47,166 --> 00:15:48,667
GET IT OFF!

277
00:15:48,709 --> 00:15:49,625
GET IT OFF!

278
00:15:58,417 --> 00:15:59,667
DON'T BOTHER.

279
00:16:01,834 --> 00:16:04,000
ZHAO, DON'T!

280
00:16:04,041 --> 00:16:05,834
IT'S MY DESTINY...

281
00:16:05,875 --> 00:16:08,083
TO DESTROY THE MOON

282
00:16:08,125 --> 00:16:09,959
AND THE WATER TRIBE.

283
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,417
DESTROYING THE MOON

284
00:16:11,458 --> 00:16:13,458
WON'T JUST HURT
THE WATER TRIBE,

285
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:15,375
IT WILL HURT EVERYONE--

286
00:16:15,417 --> 00:16:17,083
INCLUDING YOU.

287
00:16:17,125 --> 00:16:18,709
WITHOUT THE MOON,

288
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:20,875
EVERYTHING WOULD
FALL OUT OF BALANCE--

289
00:16:20,917 --> 00:16:23,083
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT KIND OF CHAOS

290
00:16:23,125 --> 00:16:24,542
THAT WOULD UNLEASH
ON THE WORLD.

291
00:16:24,583 --> 00:16:26,125
Uncle: HE'S RIGHT, ZHAO.

292
00:16:26,166 --> 00:16:28,041
GENERAL IROH,

293
00:16:28,083 --> 00:16:30,166
WHY AM I NOT
SURPRISED

294
00:16:30,208 --> 00:16:31,750
TO DISCOVER
YOUR TREACHERY.

295
00:16:31,792 --> 00:16:33,959
I'M NO TRAITOR, ZHAO.

296
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:36,125
THE FIRE NATION
NEEDS THE MOON, TOO.

297
00:16:36,166 --> 00:16:39,709
WE ALL DEPEND
ON THE BALANCE.

298
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:42,208
WHATEVER YOU DO
TO THAT SPIRIT,

299
00:16:42,250 --> 00:16:44,417
I'LL UNLEASH ON
YOU TENFOLD!

300
00:16:44,458 --> 00:16:46,000
LET IT GO NOW!

301
00:16:55,166 --> 00:16:56,583
[YELLING]

302
00:17:04,250 --> 00:17:05,917
[GRUNTING]

303
00:17:13,875 --> 00:17:15,291
[GROANING]

304
00:17:27,542 --> 00:17:30,125
THERE'S NO HOPE NOW.

305
00:17:30,166 --> 00:17:31,125
IT'S OVER.

306
00:17:33,583 --> 00:17:34,709
NO...

307
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:35,625
IT'S NOT OVER.

308
00:18:51,834 --> 00:18:53,250
YOU'RE ALIVE?!

309
00:18:53,291 --> 00:18:54,500
YOU TRIED TO
HAVE ME KILLED!

310
00:18:58,166 --> 00:19:00,041
YES, I DID.

311
00:19:00,083 --> 00:19:01,959
YOU'RE THE BLUE
SPIRIT--

312
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:04,166
AN ENEMY OF
THE FIRE NATION!

313
00:19:04,208 --> 00:19:06,166
YOU FREED THE AVATAR.

314
00:19:06,208 --> 00:19:07,083
I HAD NO CHOICE!

315
00:19:11,291 --> 00:19:14,125
YOU SHOULD HAVE CHOSEN
TO ACCEPT YOUR FAILURE,

316
00:19:14,166 --> 00:19:16,000
YOUR DISGRACE...

317
00:19:16,041 --> 00:19:19,125
THEN AT LEAST YOU
COULD HAVE LIVED.

318
00:19:19,166 --> 00:19:20,583
[GRUNTING]

319
00:19:30,083 --> 00:19:31,834
IT'S TOO LATE--

320
00:19:31,875 --> 00:19:32,667
IT'S DEAD.

321
00:19:36,834 --> 00:19:39,500
YOU HAVE BEEN TOUCHED
BY THE MOON SPIRIT.

322
00:19:39,542 --> 00:19:42,041
SOME OF ITS LIFE
IS IN YOU.

323
00:19:42,083 --> 00:19:44,417
YES, YOU'RE RIGHT...

324
00:19:44,458 --> 00:19:47,709
IT GAVE ME LIFE.

325
00:19:47,750 --> 00:19:49,083
MAYBE I CAN
GIVE IT BACK.

326
00:19:50,458 --> 00:19:51,959
NO!

327
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,000
YOU DON'T HAVE
TO DO THAT.

328
00:19:53,041 --> 00:19:55,000
IT'S MY DUTY, SOKKA.

329
00:19:55,041 --> 00:19:56,458
I WON'T LET YOU.

330
00:19:56,500 --> 00:19:58,667
YOUR FATHER TOLD
ME TO PROTECT YOU!

331
00:19:58,709 --> 00:19:59,542
I HAVE TO DO THIS.

332
00:20:12,083 --> 00:20:13,125
[GASPS]

333
00:20:13,166 --> 00:20:13,834
NO!

334
00:20:16,542 --> 00:20:18,125
SHE'S GONE.

335
00:20:18,166 --> 00:20:19,125
SHE'S GONE.

336
00:21:19,208 --> 00:21:21,166
GOOD-BYE, SOKKA.

337
00:21:21,208 --> 00:21:22,834
I'LL ALWAYS
BE WITH YOU.

338
00:21:53,250 --> 00:21:54,917
[GRUNTING]

339
00:22:02,625 --> 00:22:04,083
IT CAN'T BE!

340
00:22:14,625 --> 00:22:15,667
TAKE MY HAND!

341
00:22:32,917 --> 00:22:35,625
I'VE DECIDED TO GO
TO THE SOUTH POLE.

342
00:22:35,667 --> 00:22:36,917
SOME OTHER BENDERS
AND HEALERS

343
00:22:36,959 --> 00:22:38,792
WANT TO JOIN ME.

344
00:22:38,834 --> 00:22:41,083
IT'S TIME WE
HELPED REBUILD
OUR SISTER TRIBE.

345
00:22:41,125 --> 00:22:42,917
WHAT ABOUT AANG?

346
00:22:42,959 --> 00:22:44,917
HE STILL NEEDS TO
LEARN WATERBENDING.

347
00:22:44,959 --> 00:22:47,208
WELL--THEN HE
BETTER GET USED TO

348
00:22:47,250 --> 00:22:49,333
CALLING YOU
MASTER KATARA.

349
00:22:52,166 --> 00:22:54,208
THE SPIRITS
GAVE ME A VISION

350
00:22:54,250 --> 00:22:55,709
WHEN YUE WAS BORN.

351
00:22:55,750 --> 00:22:58,041
I SAW A BEAUTIFUL,

352
00:22:58,083 --> 00:23:03,375
BRAVE YOUNG WOMAN BECOME
THE MOON SPIRIT.

353
00:23:03,417 --> 00:23:05,083
I KNEW THIS DAY
WOULD COME.

354
00:23:05,125 --> 00:23:06,709
YOU MUST BE PROUD.

355
00:23:06,750 --> 00:23:09,041
SO PROUD...

356
00:23:09,083 --> 00:23:10,208
AND SAD.

357
00:23:12,625 --> 00:23:15,291
Uncle: I'M SURPRISED,
PRINCE ZUKO,

358
00:23:15,333 --> 00:23:17,000
SURPRISED THAT
YOU ARE NOT

359
00:23:17,041 --> 00:23:20,250
AT THIS MOMENT TRYING
TO CAPTURE THE AVATAR.

360
00:23:20,291 --> 00:23:21,875
I'M TIRED.

361
00:23:21,917 --> 00:23:24,125
THEN YOU SHOULD REST.

362
00:23:24,166 --> 00:23:26,208
A MAN NEEDS HIS REST.

363
00:23:42,166 --> 00:23:44,208
[CHITTERING]

364
00:23:44,250 --> 00:23:45,667
YOU, TOO, MOMO!

365
00:23:45,709 --> 00:23:46,709
COME HERE!

366
00:23:57,458 --> 00:24:00,083
IROH IS A TRAITOR,

367
00:24:00,125 --> 00:24:03,083
AND YOUR BROTHER ZUKO
IS A FAILURE.

368
00:24:03,125 --> 00:24:05,875
I HAVE A TASK FOR YOU...

369
00:24:16,709 --> 00:24:19,959
[MEN CHANTING RHYTHMICALLY]
